@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Cybersecurity Resources";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Cybersecurity Resources</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">
        The cybersecurity field is vital in safeguarding information and digital assets from threats and vulnerabilities. This collection of resources provides a comprehensive guide for beginners and professionals alike to excel in cybersecurity. From foundational certifications to advanced ethical hacking, these materials are curated to equip you with the knowledge and tools necessary to secure systems, networks, and data.
    </p>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">CompTIA Security+</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        CompTIA Security+ is an industry-recognized certification designed for entry-level professionals. This resource covers the basics of risk management, network security, and compliance, making it ideal for those starting a cybersecurity career.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.comptia.org/certifications/security" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Introduction to Cybersecurity</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Offered by Cisco Networking Academy, this beginner-friendly course introduces the core concepts of cybersecurity, including types of attacks, threat detection, and data protection strategies. Hands-on exercises make learning interactive and effective.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.netacad.com/courses/cybersecurity" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Certified Ethical Hacker</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        The CEH certification from EC-Council is a globally respected credential that teaches ethical hacking techniques and methodologies. Learn how to think like a hacker to identify vulnerabilities and strengthen systems against cyberattacks.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.eccouncil.org/programs/certified-ethical-hacker-ceh/" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Google Cybersecurity Training</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This free training program from Google offers hands-on exercises and certification preparation for those interested in practical cybersecurity applications. It's an excellent choice for anyone aiming to build foundational skills in securing systems and networks.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://grow.google/certificates/" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Stanford Advanced Cybersecurity Program</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Offered by Stanford University, this advanced program explores cutting-edge practices in threat analysis, risk assessment, and data protection. It's tailored for professionals seeking to deepen their expertise in the ever-evolving field of cybersecurity.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://online.stanford.edu/professional-education" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">IBM Cybersecurity Analyst Professional Certificate</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This professional certificate, hosted on Coursera, provides in-depth knowledge of security intelligence and event management (SIEM) systems, incident response, and risk analysis. With hands-on labs and real-world scenarios, this is an invaluable resource for aspiring analysts.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/ibm-cybersecurity-analyst" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
